BankPeriodClose is a BusinessTask
    owned by cb

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            Reports
                BankPeriodCloseReport

    Parameters
		CashManagementGroup   
        CashCode
        CcgCashCodeGrp          is a CashCodeGroup
        PeriodDate              is Date
        SortOption              is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                TransactionCode value is "C"
                Date            value is "D"
        UpdateOption            is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"

    Parameter Rules
        PeriodDate
            required
        SortOption
        	initial value is "C"
            default to "C"
        UpdateOption
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        CashManagementGroup
            if (CashCode entered or CcgCashCodeGrp entered)
                required

    Actions
        BankPeriodClose is a Set Action
